{"tid":2449710,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中環滙豐銀行總行今起關閉","createTime":"2021-03-17T01:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T05:15:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a66d30ea2b379806f4afca3359875f02f6136489","tid":2449710,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】中環滙豐銀行總行被納入強制檢測公告，總行今日起關閉至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n總行地下通往上層的扶手電梯暫停運作，並貼有通告指總行即日起暫停營業，地面的自動櫃員機服務正常，保安穿著全套保護衣。<br />\n<br />\n一名於滙豐銀行總行工作的資訊科技工程師周二確診，政府隨後刊憲將總行列入強制檢測大廈名單，任何人在本月3日至16日曾於大廈逗留超過兩小時要在星期五之前接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=427669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427669&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=1591d459\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427669&h=5b340ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=427669</a>"},{"pid":"56bf10d0a86e9e4d6c689192981c2d1f067f32a4","tid":2449710,"uid":186882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:36:58.000Z","msg":"匯豐又想借機炒IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc3da80bcc12c4849361319b301ca8e19bcd028","tid":2449710,"uid":8511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkdZjG4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkdZjG4.png&h=ad3a9f40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15f9640059948cf38e535b406bdf23137e62c4a2","tid":2449710,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa9d8671cd0c59106f721edb4f9b08b871841bd","tid":2449710,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r